# Simple Secure Messaging Service:
---------

Stuff, uses Public Key Crypto

# Server
---------
Models:
 User -> Main Account
 Device -> Code/Key/App
 User-User -> User makes friends(?)
 Message -> User Encrypted Message

Procedure:
 UserA request to send message to UserB
 Server grants ok for message, sends down UserBPubKey
 UserA Encrypts Message with UserBPubKey
 UserA Encrypts Message again with ServerPubKey
 UserA sends encrypted message to server
 Server decrypte with ServerPrivateKey, store encrypted message for UserB
 UserB receives encrypted message

Basically SSL Handshaking

